Package: mattech-dos
Version: 1.0.0
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, qemu-system-x86, qemu-utils, xdotool
Maintainer: MatTech <user@example.com>
Description: MatTech DOS – VirtualBox-style DOSBox frontend
 A VirtualBox-style GTK3 frontend for DOSBox. Features:
  - Left sidebar machine list, right detail panel (like VirtualBox)
  - DOS version picker with auto-detected CPU/RAM/disk requirements
  - Auto-download of install media from archive.org
  - Insert Floppy / Insert CD-ROM toolbar per drive letter
  - Supports MS-DOS 5/6, Windows 3.11, 95, 98, FreeDOS, PC-DOS
